sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / MCP Client
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant API as eval-hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>HTTPS
    participant Init as eval-runtime-init<br/>(init container)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Adapter as Benchmark Adapter<br/>(lm-eval, RAGAS, etc.)
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Model as Model Endpoint<br/>HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,OCI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Submission
    User->>RBAC: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA token)
    RBAC->>RBAC: SubjectAccessReview
    RBAC->>API: Forward request<br/>X-Tenant + X-User headers
    API->>API: Validate job config<br/>Build Job spec
    API->>K8s: Create batch/v1 Job<br/>+ ConfigMap (sidecar config)<br/>+ Secret (ref tokens)<br/>Auth: SA token
    K8s-->>API: Job created
    API->>MLflow: Create experiment (optional)<br/>Auth: Bearer token (file)
    MLflow-->>API: Experiment ID
    API-->>RBAC: 202 Accepted<br/>{job_id, status: pending}
    RBAC-->>User: HTTPS response

    Note over User,OCI: Flow 2: Evaluation Job Execution (Pod Lifecycle)
    K8s->>Init: Start init container
    Init->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>Init: Test data files
    Init-->>K8s: Init complete

    K8s->>Adapter: Start adapter container
    K8s->>Sidecar: Start sidecar (native, RestartPolicy=Always)

    loop For each benchmark
        Adapter->>Sidecar: Model inference request<br/>Auth: ref token (api-key:ref)
        Sidecar->>Sidecar: Detect ref token<br/>Inject real credentials
        Sidecar->>Model: Forward with real credentials<br/>Auth: Bearer token (from Secret)
        Model-->>Sidecar: Inference response
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: Response

        Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>Status update
        Sidecar->>RBAC: Forward status event<br/>Auth: SA token (cached 5m)
        RBAC->>API: Status event
        API-->>RBAC: OK
        RBAC-->>Sidecar: OK

        Adapter->>Sidecar: MLflow tracking calls
        Sidecar->>MLflow: Forward /api/2.0/mlflow/*<br/>Auth: Bearer token (cached 5m)
        MLflow-->>Sidecar: OK
    end

    Adapter->>Sidecar: Push artifacts (optional)
    Sidecar->>OCI: OCI Distribution v2<br/>Auth: Docker config (OAuth2)
    OCI-->>Sidecar: Push complete

    Note over User,OCI: Flow 3: MCP Client Interaction
    participant MCPProxy as kube-rbac-proxy (MCP)<br/>8443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    participant MCP as evalhub-mcp<br/>3001/TCP HTTP

    User->>MCPProxy: MCP JSON-RPC / Streamable HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA token)
    MCPProxy->>MCP: Forward<br/>X-Tenant + X-User headers
    MCP->>API: GET/POST /api/v1/evaluations/*<br/>Auth: Bearer token
    API-->>MCP: JSON response
    MCP-->>MCPProxy: MCP response
    MCPProxy-->>User: HTTPS response
